---
import Layout from '../../layouts/PostLayout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import mellaImage1 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (1).jpg';
import mellaImage2 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (2).jpg';
import mellaImage3 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (3).jpg';
import mellaImage4 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (4).jpg';
import mellaImage5 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (5).jpg';
import mellaImage6 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (6).jpg';
import mellaImage7 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (7).jpg';
import mellaImage8 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (8).jpg';
import mellaImage9 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (9).jpg';
import mellaImage10 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (10).jpg';
import mellaImage11 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (11).jpg';
import mellaImage12 from '../../assets/fixed/mella/mella (12).jpg';

const IMAGE_PROPS = {
    loading: 'lazy',
    decoding: 'async',
    class: 'w-full h-auto rounded-lg',
    width: '100%',
    height: '100%',
    formats: ['avif', 'webp', 'jpg'],
    quality: 80,
    rotate: 0
};

const postData = {
    title: 'Little Hippo - Mella',
    description: 'Tear down of the little hippo mella alarm clock',
    image: {
        url: '/assets/mella/mella (1).jpg',
        alt: 'Little Hippo Mella Alarm Clock Teardown'
    },
    pubDate: '2025-09-27',
    tags: ['teardown', 'circuit bending']
};
---

<Layout frontmatter={postData}>
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
        <div class="featured-photos mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-6">Featured Images</h2>
            <div class="flex justify-center">
                <figure class="m-0">
                    <Image src={mellaImage1} alt="Little Hippo Mella - Front View" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
                    <figcaption class="text-sm text-center mt-2 text-gray-600">Front View</figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p>
            I will be tearing down the little hippo mella alarm clock. I will be posting the teardown process, the circuit bending process, and the audio of the
            clock. I will also briefly write about what needs to be done to access the firmware and what type of chips are on the board.
        </p>

        <h2>Teardown</h2>

        <p>Here's a look at the initial teardown process:</p>

        <figure class="my-6">
            <Image src={mellaImage4} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="my-8">
            <Image src={mellaImage5} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="my-8">
            <Image src={mellaImage6} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="my-8">
            <Image src={mellaImage7} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="my-8">
            <Image src={mellaImage8} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="my-8">
            <Image src={mellaImage9} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="my-8">
            <Image src={mellaImage10} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="my-8">
            <Image src={mellaImage11} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <figure class="my-8">
            <Image src={mellaImage12} alt="Mella teardown in progress" {...IMAGE_PROPS} />
            <figcaption class="mt-2 italic text-gray-600 text-center">The Mella alarm clock during teardown</figcaption>
        </figure>

        <p></p>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .prose {
        max-width: 65ch;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .prose :where(h2):not(:where([class~='not-prose'] *)) {
        margin-top: 1.5em;
        margin-bottom: 0.75em;
        line-height: 1.5;
        font-weight: 600;
    }
    .featured-photos {
        margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .featured-photos {
            margin: 1rem 0;
        }
    }
</style>
